description:
An amateur astronomer was filming the moon when he spotted multiple UFOs flying past. It's not clear what these objects might be, but they all seemed to be travelling at the same speed, almost in pairs. Could this be space debris, almost all UFOs spotted in space seem to be instantly dismissed as space debris these days. I guess our skies are are full of rubbish as our oceans 🤷‍♂️.
